<h2><u>Mosteller equation</u></h2>


<p>In the previous section, the BSA was calculated based on nomogram (DuBois and DuBois formula). While this remains the most popular method to estimate BSA, 
an easier method to calculate BSA for adults is the Mosteller equation: </p>
     
     
     <div class="formulae"><p>$$ BSA \ m^2 = \sqrt{Ht \ (cm) \times Wt \ (kg) \over 3600} $$</p></div>
     
